{"word":"ποίημα","slug":"ποίημα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ποίημα</b></el> <el>(ποίημα, ατος, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ποιέω'><el>ποιέω</el></a>\n<p/><i>anything made</i> or <i>done;</i> hence,<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a work</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a poetical work, poem</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a deed, act</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}